---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="OUTLYR — Built Not Born">

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero" style="border-top:none; padding-top:0;">
  <div class="hero-grid">
    <span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
    <span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
    <span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
  </div>
  <span class="hero-bg-word" id="heroBgWord">OUTLYR</span>
  <div class="hero-body">
    <p class="hero-kicker">// Not for everyone</p>
    <h1 class="hero-h1">
      Built<br><span class="g"><em>Not Born.</em></span>
    </h1>
    <div class="hero-statement">
      <p>
        For those who understand that <strong>who you are is not what you were given</strong> —
        it is what you have chosen, earned, and are still in the process of becoming.
        No audience required.
      </p>
      <a href="#cta" class="hero-cta">
        Apply to The Circle <span>↗</span>
      </a>
    </div>
        
  </div>
  <span class="hero-index">OUTLYR — 001 / 005 — IDENTITY</span>
</section>

<!-- BELIEF -->
<section class="belief reveal">
  <div class="belief-left">
    <p class="tag">01 — The Belief</p>
    <h2>Your ceiling<br>is <em>yours.</em></h2>
  </div>
  <div class="belief-right reveal">
    <div class="belief-line">
      <p>
        A quiet conviction that most people never fully test —
        <strong>that what you can become is largely self-determined.</strong>
        The variable is not talent, not birth, not circumstance.
        It is how much you are genuinely willing to put in.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="belief-line">
      <p>
        You already know this. You've known it for a while.
        <strong>That's why you're still here, still at it</strong> — long after
        the people who started with you found reasons to stop.
        Outlyr doesn't give you this belief. It recognises it in you.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ONE LEVEL DEEPER -->
<section class="deeper">
  <div class="deeper-top reveal">
    <div>
      <p class="tag">02 — The Marker</p>
      <h2>One level<br><em>deeper.</em></h2>
    </div>
    <p class="deeper-intro">
      The Outlyr mind doesn't react — it analyzes.
      Doesn't judge — it understands.<br><br>
      <strong>When everyone else has an opinion, the Outlyr person has a question:</strong>
      why is this happening, what does it reveal, what can be learned from it.
      That instinct — to go one level below the surface — is the sharpest marker of this tribe.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="contrast reveal">
    <div class="contrast-col">
      <p class="contrast-label">Everyone else</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Reacts to what happened</li>
        <li>Judges the person</li>
        <li>Talks about events</li>
        <li>Performs the journey</li>
        <li>Builds for the audience</li>
        <li>Stops when it gets hard</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="contrast-col">
      <p class="contrast-label">The Outlyr mind</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Asks why it happened</li>
        <li>Studies the pattern</li>
        <li>Talks about ideas</li>
        <li>Lives the process quietly</li>
        <li>Builds for themselves</li>
        <li>Gets interesting when it gets hard</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="domains">
    <div class="domain reveal">
      <p class="domain-num">01</p>
      <h3>The Founder</h3>
      <p>Building something from nothing, in a space where nobody in their circle has done it before.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="domain reveal">
      <p class="domain-num">02</p>
      <h3>The Aspirant</h3>
      <p>Years of preparation, no guarantee, no shortcut — just the decision that this is the thing and this is the commitment.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="domain reveal">
      <p class="domain-num">03</p>
      <h3>The Creator</h3>
      <p>Building a body of work in a field where the path isn't linear and the validation doesn't come early.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="domain reveal">
      <p class="domain-num">04</p>
      <h3>The Athlete</h3>
      <p>Choosing a physical standard and holding it — not for competition, but because the discipline itself is the point.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CONVICTION QUOTE -->
<section class="conviction reveal">
  <blockquote>
    "Identity is not inherited.<br>It is chosen, and then it is earned."
  </blockquote>
  <p class="conviction-sub">
    What you were born into — family, city, circumstance —
    that is the starting point. Not the ending one.
    In a country where birth is still widely treated as destiny,
    choosing otherwise is not just personal.<br>It is a position.
  </p>
  <cite>— The Outlyr Manifesto</cite>
</section>

<!-- COMMUNITY -->
<section class="community" id="community">
  <div class="community-top reveal">
    <div>
      <p class="tag">03 — The Circle</p>
      <h2>The room<br>where it<br><em>goes somewhere.</em></h2>
    </div>
    <p class="community-desc">
      Most conversations end where they started.
      An opinion formed, a reaction shared, a scroll continued.<br><br>
      <strong>The Circle is built for conversations that go somewhere.</strong>
      Ideas examined, challenged, built upon. Implementation discussed, not just admired.
      A private room of people who are actually in the process — not planning to be, not narrating it for an audience.
      Actually in it.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="room-statement reveal">
    <h3>Ideas.<br>Not <em>gossip.</em></h3>
    <p>
      The Circle has one social currency — <strong>depth of thinking and bias toward building.</strong>
      The founder in Nagpur, the aspirant in Patna, the artist in New York, the athlete in Pune —
      they don't share a domain. They share a quality of mind.
      That is what the room is built on. That is what it protects.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="pillars">
    <div class="pillar reveal">
      <span class="pillar-num">I</span>
      <h3>The Lab</h3>
      <p>A private space where people who are building things talk to other people who are building things. Not about motivation — about the actual process. The decisions, the contradictions, the things that are working and the things that aren't.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pillar reveal">
      <span class="pillar-num">II</span>
      <h3>Behind the Build</h3>
      <p>Members document their process in real time — the decisions, the pivots, the failures, the breakthroughs. Not polished case studies. Raw, ongoing records of what it actually looks like to build something from the inside.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pillar reveal">
      <span class="pillar-num">III</span>
      <h3>The Right Room</h3>
      <p>Filtered entry. Not by achievement, not by credentials, not by following count. By quality of thinking and direction of movement. The room is only as valuable as the people inside it — and that standard never drops.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="cta" id="cta">
  <p class="cta-tag reveal">// Enter</p>
  <h2 class="reveal">
    Live Your<br>
    Way <em>In.</em>
  </h2>
  <p class="cta-body reveal">
    The Circle is not open to everyone. It is not open to most people.<br><br>
    <strong>Entry is reviewed. Standards are held.</strong>
    We are looking for a rare kind of person — not the most successful,
    not the most followed, not the most impressive.
    The ones who think deepest and are moving toward something real.
    If that is you, you already know it.
    Start here.
  </p>
  <div>
  <a href="/the-circle" class="cta-apply-btn reveal">
    Apply to The Circle <span>↗</span>
  </a>
  </div>

  <a href="https://instagram.com/outlyr.in" target="_blank" class="cta-insta reveal">
    Follow the build &nbsp;<span class="handle">@outlyr.in</span>
  </a>
</section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>

  @keyframes up {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(32px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  @keyframes fadeIn { to { opacity: 1; } }

  .hero {
    min-height: 100svh;
    display: grid; grid-template-rows: 1fr auto;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    padding: 0 56px;
  }
  .hero-grid {
    position: absolute; inset: 0; pointer-events: none;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
  }
  .hero-grid span { border-right: 1px solid var(--a10); }
  .hero-grid span:first-child { border-left: 1px solid var(--a10); }

  .hero-bg-word {
    position: absolute; bottom: -0.05em; right: -0.02em;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(22vw, 28vw, 34vw);
    line-height: 0.85; color: transparent;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgba(200,184,154,0.03);
    pointer-events: none; user-select: none;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em; z-index: 1; will-change: transform;
  }
  .hero-body {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-end; padding-bottom: 80px;
    position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: 900px;
  }
  .hero-kicker {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.28em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--acc); margin-bottom: 36px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px;
    opacity: 0; animation: up 0.7s ease forwards 0.2s;
  }
  .hero-kicker::before {
    content: ''; width: 32px; height: 1px;
    background: var(--a40); display: block;
  }
  .hero-h1 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(96px, 14vw, 210px);
    line-height: 0.86; letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    opacity: 0; animation: up 1s ease forwards 0.4s;
  }
  .hero-h1 .g { color: var(--acc); }
  .hero-h1 .o {
    color: transparent;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgba(237,232,225,0.25);
  }
  .hero-statement {
    margin-top: 52px; max-width: 600px;
    opacity: 0; animation: up 0.8s ease forwards 0.75s;
  }
  .hero-statement p {
    font-size: clamp(22px, 2.2vw, 28px);
    line-height: 1.68; font-style: italic; color: var(--t55);
  }
  .hero-statement p strong { color: var(--tx); font-style: normal; font-weight: 600; }
  .hero-index {
    position: absolute; right: 56px; bottom: 80px;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    color: var(--t30); z-index: 2; writing-mode: vertical-rl;
    opacity: 0; animation: fadeIn 1s ease forwards 1.2s;
  }

  .hero-footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--a10);
    padding: 20px 0;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center; position: relative; z-index: 2;
    opacity: 0; animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease forwards 1.4s;
  }
  .hero-footer span {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--t30);
  }

  .hero-cta {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px;
  border: 1px solid var(--a40);
  padding: 18px 48px;
  font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.28em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--acc); text-decoration: none;
  transition: background 0.3s, border-color 0.3s, color 0.3s;
  margin-top: 52px;
  opacity: 0; animation: up 0.8s ease forwards 1.1s;
  position: relative; z-index: 2;
}
.hero-cta:hover {
  background: var(--a05);
  border-color: var(--acc);
  color: var(--tx);
}
.hero-cta span {
  font-size: 14px;
  transition: transform 0.3s;
}
.hero-cta:hover span { transform: translate(3px, -3px); }

  @keyframes up {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(32px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  @keyframes fadeIn { to { opacity: 1; } }

  .tag {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.28em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--acc);
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px;
  }
  .tag::before {
    content: ''; width: 24px; height: 1px;
    background: var(--a40); display: block; flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  section {
    padding: 128px 56px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--a10);
    position: relative;
  }

  .belief {
    background: var(--bg2);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px; align-items: center;
  }

  .belief-left h2 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(56px, 7vw, 108px);
    line-height: 0.88; letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    margin-top: 28px;
  }
  .belief-left h2 em { color: var(--acc); font-style: italic; }

  .belief-right {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 32px;
  }

  .belief-line {
    padding: 32px 36px;
    border: 1px solid var(--a10);
    position: relative;
    transition: border-color 0.4s, background 0.4s;
  }
  .belief-line:hover {
    border-color: var(--a20);
    background: var(--a05);
  }
  .belief-line::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 2px; height: 0;
    background: var(--acc);
    transition: height 0.5s ease;
  }
  .belief-line:hover::before { height: 100%; }

  .belief-line p {
    font-size: clamp(22px, 2.0vw, 25px);
    line-height: 1.75; font-style: italic;
    color: var(--t55);
  }
  .belief-line p strong {
    color: var(--tx); font-style: normal; font-weight: 600;
  }

  .deeper-top {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px; margin-bottom: 88px; align-items: end;
  }

  .deeper-top h2 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(56px, 7vw, 108px);
    line-height: 0.88; letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    margin-top: 28px;
  }
  .deeper-top h2 em { color: var(--acc); font-style: italic; }

  .deeper-intro {
    font-size: clamp(22px, 2.0vw, 25px);
    line-height: 1.78; font-style: italic;
    color: var(--t55); padding-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .deeper-intro strong { color: var(--tx); font-style: normal; font-weight: 600; }

  .contrast {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    border: 1px solid var(--a10);
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .contrast-col { padding: 52px 48px; }
  .contrast-col:first-child { border-right: 1px solid var(--a10); }

  .contrast-label {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.28em; text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .contrast-col:first-child .contrast-label { color: var(--t30); }
  .contrast-col:last-child .contrast-label { color: var(--acc); }

  .contrast-col ul {
    list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px;
  }
  .contrast-col ul li {
    font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.7;
    font-style: italic; color: var(--t30);
    padding-left: 20px; position: relative;
  }
  .contrast-col:last-child ul li { color: var(--t55); }
  .contrast-col ul li::before {
    content: '—'; position: absolute; left: 0;
    color: var(--a40);
  }

  .domains {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .domain {
    padding: 44px 36px;
    border: 1px solid var(--a10);
    transition: background 0.4s, border-color 0.4s;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .domain:hover { background: var(--a05); border-color: var(--a20); }
  .domain::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 1px; background: var(--acc);
    transform: scaleX(0); transform-origin: left;
    transition: transform 0.5s ease;
  }
  .domain:hover::after { transform: scaleX(1); }

  .domain-num {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    color: var(--acc); margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .domain h3 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--tx); margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .domain p {
    font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--t30); font-style: italic;
  }

  .conviction {
    background: var(--bg2);
    text-align: center; overflow: hidden;
    padding: 160px 56px;
  }

  .conviction::before {
    content: '"';
    position: absolute; top: -80px; left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 480px; line-height: 1;
    color: rgba(200,184,154,0.03);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .conviction blockquote {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(30px, 3.5vw, 48px);
    font-style: italic; font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.45; color: var(--tx);
    max-width: 840px; margin: 0 auto 20px;
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }
  .conviction blockquote em { color: var(--acc); }

  .conviction-sub {
    font-size: clamp(20px, 1.8vw, 22px);
    line-height: 1.7; font-style: italic;
    color: var(--t30); max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto 40px; position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }

  .conviction cite {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--a40);
    font-style: normal; position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }

  .community-top {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px; margin-bottom: 88px; align-items: end;
  }

  .community-top h2 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(56px, 7vw, 108px);
    line-height: 0.88; letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    margin-top: 28px;
  }
  .community-top h2 em { color: var(--acc); font-style: italic; }

  .community-desc {
    font-size: clamp(22px, 2.0vw, 25px);
    line-height: 1.78; font-style: italic;
    color: var(--t55); padding-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .community-desc strong { color: var(--tx); font-style: normal; font-weight: 600; }

  .room-statement {
    border: 1px solid var(--a10);
    padding: 52px 56px;
    margin-bottom: 3px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
    gap: 64px; align-items: center;
  }

  .room-statement h3 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 56px; letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    line-height: 0.9; color: var(--tx);
  }
  .room-statement h3 em { color: var(--acc); font-style: italic; }

  .room-statement p {
    font-size: clamp(19px, 1.7vw, 22px);
    line-height: 1.78; font-style: italic; color: var(--t55);
  }
  .room-statement p strong { color: var(--tx); font-style: normal; font-weight: 600; }

  .pillars { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .pillar {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 56px 200px 1fr;
    align-items: start; gap: 48px;
    padding: 44px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--a10);
    transition: padding-left 0.4s ease;
  }
  .pillar:first-child { border-top: 1px solid var(--a10); }
  .pillar:hover { padding-left: 8px; }

  .pillar-num {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    color: var(--acc); padding-top: 4px;
  }
  .pillar h3 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 36px; letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--tx); line-height: 1;
  }
  .pillar p {
    font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--t55); font-style: italic;
  }

  .india-strip {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--a10);
    padding: 56px;
    background: var(--bg3);
    display: flex; align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between; gap: 48px;
  }

  .india-left { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 32px; }

  .india-line {
    width: 1px; height: 64px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, var(--a40), transparent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .india-text {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(18px, 2vw, 26px);
    font-style: italic; color: var(--t55);
    line-height: 1.5; max-width: 600px;
  }
  .india-text em { color: var(--acc); font-style: italic; }

  .india-mono {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--t30);
    white-space: nowrap; flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .cta {
    padding: 160px 56px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cta::before {
    content: 'OUTLYR';
    position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 30vw; letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: transparent;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgba(200,184,154,0.03);
    pointer-events: none; white-space: nowrap;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .cta-tag {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.32em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--acc);
    margin-bottom: 40px; position: relative;
  }

  .cta h2 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(72px, 11vw, 160px);
    line-height: 0.88; letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 40px; position: relative;
  }
  .cta h2 em { color: var(--acc); font-style: italic; }
  .cta h2 .o {
    color: transparent;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgba(237,232,225,0.2);
  }

  .cta-body {
    font-size: clamp(17px, 1.5vw, 20px);
    font-style: italic; color: var(--t55);
    max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto 64px;
    line-height: 1.78; position: relative;
  }
  .cta-body strong { color: var(--tx); font-style: normal; font-weight: 600; }

  .cta-form {
    display: flex; max-width: 460px;
    margin: 0 auto 18px; position: relative;
  }
  .cta-form input {
    flex: 1; background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid var(--a20); border-right: none;
    padding: 16px 22px; color: var(--tx);
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }
  .cta-form input::placeholder { color: var(--t30); }
